la]] || 1956\u20131978\n|-\n|| [[Frank Hawkins (Australian politician)|Frank Hawkins]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Newcastle|Newcastle]] || 1935\u20131968\n|-\n|| [[Eric Hearnshaw]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Eastwood|Eastwood]] || 1945\u20131965\n|-\n|| [[Bob Heffron]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Maroubra|Maroubra]] || 1930\u20131968\n|-\n|| [[Pat Hills]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Phillip|Phillip]] || 1954\u20131988\n|-\n|| [[Davis Hughes]] || Country || [[Electoral district of Armidale|Armidale]] || 1950\u20131953, 1956\u20131973\n|-\n|| [[David Hunter (New South Wales politician)|David Hunter]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Ashfield-Croydon|Ashfield-Croydon]] || 1940\u20131976\n|-\n|| [[Harold Jackson (Australian politician)|Harold Jackson]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Gosford|Gosford]] || 1950\u20131965\n|-\n|| [[Rex Jackson]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Bulli|Bulli]] || 1955\u20131986\n|-\n|| [[Les Jordan]] || Country/Liberal {{ref label|2|2|2}} || [[Electoral district of Oxley (New South Wales)|Oxley]] || 1944\u20131965\n|-\n|| [[Gus Kelly (politician)|Gus Kelly]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Bathurst|Bathurst]] || 1925\u20131932, 1935\u20131967\n|-\n|| [[Joe Kelly (New South Wales politician)|Joe Kelly]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of East Hills|East Hills]] || 1956\u20131973\n|-\n|| Hon [[Bill Lamb]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Granville|Granville]] || 1938\u20131962\n|-\n|| Hon [[Abe Landa]] || Labor || [[Electoral district of Bondi|Bondi]] || 1930\u20131965\t\n|-\n|| [[Walter Lawrence]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Drummoyne|Drummoyne]] || 1956\u20131962\n|-\n|| [[Joe Lawson (politician)|Joe Lawson]] || Country || [[Electoral district of Murray|Murray]] || 1932\u20131973\n|-\n|| [[Tom Lewis (Australian politician)|Tom Lewis]] || Liberal || [[Electoral district of Wollondilly|Wollondilly]] || 1957\u20131978\n|-\n|| Hon [[Ray Maher]] || Labor || [[Electoral district o